pokedexEntries.ruby: Aggron claims an entire mountain as its own territory. It mercilessly beats up anything that violates its environment. This Pokémon vigilantly patrols its territory at all times.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Aggron is surprisingly protective of its environment. If its mountain is ravaged by a landslide or a fire, this Pokémon will haul topsoil to the area, plant trees, and beautifully restore its own territory.
pokedexEntries.emerald: Its iron horns grow longer a little at a time. They are used to determine the Aggron's age. The gouges in its armor are worn with pride as mementos from battles.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: It claims a large mountain as its sole territory. It mercilessly thrashes those that violate its space.
